NAME
     upson - Starts powerfail shutdown sequence

SYNOPSIS
     upson

DESCRIPTION
   Discussion
     The upson command starts the system powerfail procedure via
     a write to /dev/ups. The init process is sent SIGPWR, a
     warning message is written to the system log, and forced
     write mode is enabled.

FILES
     /dev/ups

